Mortgage Calculator Program
created by: Heather Pratt
email: kitty.ghoul1@gmail.com

Simple mortgage calculator program
To use, enter prompted amounts of principal, interest and term. 
###There is no validation yet.  Improper input will crash the program.
###Fix coming in later release

Once entered, the monthly payment will be displayed.
Prompt given for amortization.  If 'y', amortization displays

any other response will exit the program.  
